    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/8224cbe58134f0d1f4155da1555830f9.poster.avif?t=1755453362\" width=628 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/8224cbe58134f0d1f4155da1555830f9.webm?t=1755453362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/8224cbe58134f0d1f4155da1555830f9.mp4?t=1755453362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><i><u>You think you can just escape out of this house? Hahahaha.... NO!</u></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/233b0e90bb41e79a2bb38d3362d0d9a8.poster.avif?t=1755453362\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/233b0e90bb41e79a2bb38d3362d0d9a8.webm?t=1755453362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/233b0e90bb41e79a2bb38d3362d0d9a8.mp4?t=1755453362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>The Story about this game:</u></strong></h2>You are a <strong>detective</strong> who has just <strong>returned</strong> to the house where the <strong>Smith</strong> family lived, because your <strong>grandparents</strong> are <strong>missing</strong> and this was their <strong>last</strong> address and so you decided to <strong>find</strong> them. But what you don't know is that this <strong>decision</strong> is going to be a<strong> horror trip</strong> for you. Because this house is <strong>not empty</strong> and the Smiths <strong>still live</strong> here. By <strong>solving</strong> the <strong>puzzles</strong> and <strong>mysteries</strong> in this horror house you get all the <strong>informations</strong> about the Smith family, what is happening here and about your grandparents. But don’t <strong>lose</strong> yourself along the way and, most <strong>importantly</strong> TRY TO <strong>SURVIVE</strong>! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/f45e735fead442053060c6aa9fa9c037.avif?t=1755453362\" width=628 height=354 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/c40aaaac2d81f7e18d3ffb8c568e60e1.avif?t=1755453362\" width=629 height=201 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>What is this game?</u></strong></h2>Seductive Solitude is a <strong>horror game</strong> that will keep you on the edge of your seat. It's <strong>scary</strong>, but it's also <strong>full</strong> of <strong>suspense and surprises</strong>. You'll <strong>never</strong> know what's going to happen next. And that's what makes it so <strong>exciting</strong>. You're never quite sure what's real and what's not. Is the house really <strong>empty</strong>, or is there something <strong>lurking</strong> in the <strong>shadows</strong>? And what's up with that doll and the <strong>other guys</strong>? The longer you stay in the house, the weirder the things that happen there. SO GET OUT FAST!<br><br><i><u>YOU WILL DIE!</u></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/52ac75b4135d6bea5cc0311965d25dae.avif?t=1755453362\" width=628 height=354 /></span><br><br><br>Seductive Solitude is split into 3 chapters:<br><strong><u>Chapter 1</u></strong><br>The (empty) house<br>-----------------------<br><strong><u>Chapter 2</u></strong><br>Don't worry this is just the beginning<br>-----------------